---
// src/pages/about.astro
import Layout from '../components/layout/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="How We Build eLearning Without the Drama | The eLearning Company"
  description="Learn about our streamlined 3-week process for custom eLearning development. 15+ years of experience, transparent pricing, and zero project management overhead."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="about-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="page-title">How We Build eLearning Without the Drama</h1>
      <p class="page-subtitle">We've built hundreds of courses for Australian organisations. Along the way, we learned that most L&D teams don't need another complex agency relationship—they need a reliable partner who delivers on time and on budget.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Story Section -->
  <section class="story-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="story-content">
        <h2>Why We Started This</h2>
        <p>After years developing eLearning for organisations of all sizes, we noticed a pattern: the traditional agency model wasn't working.</p>
        
        <p>eLearning agencies were charging $20,000-$35,000 per course (sometimes more!) and taking 8-12 weeks to deliver. Projects involved endless meetings, complex project management overhead, and uneccessary change requests at the tail end of the project.</p>
        
        <p>Meanwhile, clients just wanted:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Professional courses that work</li>
          <li>Clear pricing from day one</li>
          <li>Fast delivery without sacrificing quality</li>
          <li>Minimal time investment from their team</li>
        </ul>

        <p>So we built something different: a streamlined eLearning development service that delivers agency-quality courses in 3 weeks, with transparent pricing and none of the complexity.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What Makes Us Different -->
  <section class="different-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">What Makes Us Different</h2>
      
      <div class="different-grid">
        <div class="different-card">
          <div class="card-icon">💎</div>
          <h3>We're Transparent</h3>
          <p>No hidden costs. No vague timelines. No "it depends." All our pricing is published on our website. What we quote is what you pay.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="different-card">
          <div class="card-icon">⚡</div>
          <h3>We're Efficient</h3>
          <p>We've stripped out unnecessary meetings, endless revision cycles, and project management overhead. What remains is a streamlined process that works.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="different-card">
          <div class="card-icon">🎯</div>
          <h3>We're Practical</h3>
          <p>We deliver what works, not what wins design awards. Effective learning over fancy features. Professional quality without unnecessary complexity.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="different-card">
          <div class="card-icon">✅</div>
          <h3>We're Reliable</h3>
          <p>We say 3 weeks, we deliver in 3 weeks. No excuses, no delays. We've built a process that's predictable and repeatable.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Process in Detail -->
  <section class="process-detail-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Our 3-Week Process in Detail</h2>
      
      <div class="process-timeline">
        
        <!-- Step 1 -->
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker">
            <div class="marker-number">1</div>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3>Initial Contact & Scoping</h3>
            <div class="timeline-details">
              <p><strong>What happens:</strong> You submit a quote request or contact us directly.</p>
              <p><strong>Response time:</strong> Within 24 hours (usually much faster)</p>
              <p><strong>Discovery call:</strong> Quick 15-20 minute call to understand your needs</p>
              <p><strong>Quote delivery:</strong> Fixed-price quote provided immediately after call</p>
              <p><strong>Your time investment:</strong> 15-20 minutes</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 2 -->
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker">
            <div class="marker-number">2</div>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3>Project Kickoff (Week 1, Day 1)</h3>
            <div class="timeline-details">
              <p><strong>What happens:</strong> You accept the quote</p>
              <p><strong>Kickoff call:</strong> 30-min structured call to gather everything we need</p>
              <p><strong>We discuss:</strong></p>
              <ul>
                <li>Learning objectives and success criteria</li>
                <li>Target audience and their context</li>
                <li>Content review (what you have vs. what we need)</li>
                <li>Visual style preferences and branding</li>
                <li>Assessment approach and pass criteria</li>
                <li>Delivery timeline confirmation</li>
              </ul>
              <p><strong>Your time investment:</strong> 30 mins</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 3 -->
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker">
            <div class="marker-number">3</div>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3>First Draft Development (Week 1)</h3>
            <div class="timeline-details">
              <p><strong>What we do:</strong> Build the complete first draft of your course</p>
              <p><strong>What you do:</strong> Nothing! We work independently</p>
              <p><strong>Delivery:</strong> By start of Week 2</p>
              <p><strong>Format:</strong> You receive a review link to access the course</p>
              <p><strong>Your time investment:</strong> Zero during this phase</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 4 -->
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker">
            <div class="marker-number">4</div>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3>Review & Revisions (Weeks 2-3)</h3>
            <div class="timeline-details">
              <p><strong>How it works:</strong> Unlimited revisions during this 2-week window</p>
              <p><strong>Review process:</strong></p>
              <ul>
                <li>Access course via review link we provide</li>
                <li>Involve as many reviewers as needed (no extra cost)</li>
                <li>All feedback submitted via review link (keeps it organized)</li>
                <li>One designated decision-maker to resolve conflicts</li>
              </ul>
              <p><strong>Revision turnaround:</strong> We update as you leave feedback so you can always see the most up-to-date version</p>
              <p><strong>Most common:</strong> Clients only need 1-2 revision rounds</p>
              <p><strong>Your time investment:</strong> 1-3 hours total for reviews</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 5 -->
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker">
            <div class="marker-number">5</div>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3>Final Delivery (End of Week 3)</h3>
            <div class="timeline-details">
              <p><strong>What you receive:</strong></p>
              <ul>
                <li>SCORM 1.2 and 2004 packages (tested)</li>
                <li>Source files/Transfer of project </li>
                <li>Any additional assets used</li>
              </ul>
              <p><strong>Payment:</strong> We invoice at project commence with payment terms of 14 days. This can be adjusted depending on your needs/procurement policy.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="process-summary">
        <h3>Total Time Investment from You:</h3>
        <p><strong>3-5 hours over 3 weeks</strong> - That's it. We handle the heavy lifting.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Who We Work With -->
  <section class="clients-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Who We Work With</h2>
      
      <div class="clients-grid">
        <div class="client-card">
          <h3>Organisations</h3>
          <p>Mid to large Australian organisations (200-2000 employees) across all industries</p>
        </div>

        <div class="client-card">
          <h3>Teams</h3>
          <p>HR departments, L&D teams, People & Culture functions—anyone responsible for training</p>
        </div>

        <div class="client-card">
          <h3>Situations</h3>
          <p>New to eLearning, scaling training programs, or just lost your internal eLearning person</p>
        </div>

        <div class="client-card">
          <h3>Values</h3>
          <p>Organisations that value efficiency, transparency, and getting things done without drama</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="industries-note">
        <h3>Industries We've Served</h3>
        <p>Healthcare • Finance • Retail • Construction • Technology • Government • Manufacturing • Education • Professional Services • Hospitality • Agriculture • Mining • Energy • Transport • And more</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Guarantee -->
  <section class="guarantee-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="guarantee-card">
        <h2>Our Guarantee to You</h2>
        
        <div class="guarantees-grid">
          <div class="guarantee-item">
            <span class="guarantee-icon">⏰</span>
            <h4>3-Week Delivery</h4>
            <p>We commit to 3 weeks from kickoff.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="guarantee-item">
            <span class="guarantee-icon">💰</span>
            <h4>Fixed Pricing</h4>
            <p>What we quote is what you pay. No scope creep, no surprise fees, no exceptions.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="guarantee-item">
            <span class="guarantee-icon">🔄</span>
            <h4>Unlimited Revisions</h4>
            <p>During weeks 2-3, we'll revise as many times as needed until you're happy.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="guarantee-item">
            <span class="guarantee-icon">📦</span>
            <h4>Source Files Included</h4>
            <p>You get the source files. You own your course completely.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="guarantee-item">
            <span class="guarantee-icon">✅</span>
            <h4>Quality Assurance</h4>
            <p>Every course is tested before delivery. We catch issues before you do.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="guarantee-item">
            <span class="guarantee-icon">💬</span>
            <h4>Clear Communication</h4>
            <p>Responses within 24 hours. No ghosting, no waiting days for answers.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Approach to Quality -->
  <section class="quality-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Our Approach to Quality</h2>
      
      <div class="quality-content">
        <div class="quality-item">
          <h3>Effective Learning Design</h3>
          <p>We focus on learning outcomes, not feature lists. Clean structure, clear objectives, appropriate interactivity. Adult learning principles applied consistently.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="quality-item">
          <h3>Professional Visual Design</h3>
          <p>Modern, clean design using contemporary templates and styling. Professional stock imagery. Consistent branding. Responsive across all devices.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="quality-item">
          <h3>Why This Approach Works</h3>
          <p>Learners care about clear, effective training they can complete quickly. Stakeholders care about results and ROI. Nobody needs custom animations to learn workplace safety.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Experience -->
  <section class="experience-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Our Experience</h2>
      
      <div class="experience-stats">
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-number">15+</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Years of Experience</div>
        </div>

        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-number">100s</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Courses Delivered</div>
        </div>

        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-number">Over 25 common</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Training Categories</div>
        </div>

        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-number">3</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Week Delivery</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="experience-content">
        <p>We've developed eLearning across every industry you can imagine. Compliance training for healthcare. Safety training for construction. Onboarding for tech startups. Product training for retail. Sales enablement for finance.</p>
        
        <p>What we've learned: Good instructional design transcends industry. The principles of effective learning are universal. What matters is understanding your content and your audience—not having built 50 courses in your exact sub-sector.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Final CTA -->
  <section class="final-cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-card">
        <h2>Ready to Work Together?</h2>
        <p>Let's start talking about your training needs.</p>
        <div class="cta-buttons">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Get a Quote</a>
          <a href="/pricing" class="btn-secondary">View Pricing</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Hero */
  .about-hero {
    padding: 100px 0 60px;
    background: var(--bg-primary);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .page-title {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .page-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* Story Section */
  .story-section {
    padding: 80px 0;
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
  }

  .story-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .story-content h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .story-content p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .story-content ul {
    margin: 24px 0 24px 32px;
  }

  .story-content li {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  /* Different Section */
  .different-section {
    padding: 80px 0;
    background: var(--bg-primary);
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
  }

  .different-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 32px;
  }

  .different-card {
    background: var(--bg-tertiary);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 40px;
    text-align: center;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .different-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    border-color: var(--accent-primary);
  }

  .card-icon {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .different-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .different-card p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* Process Detail */
  .process-detail-section {
    padding: 80px 0;
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
  }

  .process-timeline {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .timeline-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: 32px;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  .timeline-marker {
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .marker-number {
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    background: var(--accent-gradient);
    color: white;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
  }

  .timeline-content h3 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .timeline-details p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .timeline-details strong {
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .timeline-details ul {
    margin: 12px 0 16px 24px;
  }

  .timeline-details li {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .process-summary {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.1) 0%, rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1) 100%);
    border: 2px solid var(--accent-primary);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 40px;
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 60px;
  }

  .process-summary h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .process-summary p {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .process-summary strong {
    color: var(--accent-primary);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }

  /* Clients Section */
  .clients-section {
    padding: 80px 0;
    background: var(--bg-primary);
  }

  .clients-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 32px;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
  }

  .client-card {
    background: var(--bg-tertiary);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 32px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .client-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent-primary);
  }

  .client-card p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .industries-note {
    background: var(--bg-tertiary);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 40px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .industries-note h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .industries-note p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
  }

  /* Guarantee Section */
  .guarantee-section {
    padding: 80px 0;
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
  }

  .guarantee-card {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.05) 0%, rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.05) 100%);
    border: 2px solid var(--accent-primary);
    border-radius: 24px;
    padding: 60px;
  }

  .guarantee-card h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  .guarantees-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 32px;
  }

  .guarantee-item {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .guarantee-icon {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .guarantee-item h4 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .guarantee-item p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* Quality Section */
  .quality-section {
    padding: 80px 0;
    background: var(--bg-primary);
  }

  .quality-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 32px;
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .quality-item {
    background: var(--bg-tertiary);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 32px;
  }

  .quality-item h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .quality-item p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* Experience Section */
  .experience-section {
    padding: 80px 0;
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
  }

  .experience-stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 32px;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
  }

  .stat-card {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .stat-number {
    font-size: 4rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    background: var(--accent-gradient);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .experience-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .experience-content p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  /* Final CTA */
  .final-cta-section {
    padding: 80px 0;
    background: var(--bg-primary);
  }

  .cta-card {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.15) 0%, rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.15) 100%);
    border: 2px solid var(--accent-primary);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 60px 40px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta-card h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    font-weight: 800;
  }

  .cta-card p {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn-primary,
  .btn-secondary {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 14px 32px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 700;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--accent-gradient);
    color: white;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 24px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.5);
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    background: var(--bg-tertiary);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    border: 2px solid var(--border-color);
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent-primary);
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .page-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .timeline-item {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .guarantees-grid,
    .quality-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .guarantee-card {
      padding: 40px 24px;
    }

    .cta-buttons {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .btn-primary,
    .btn-secondary {
      width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>